'''West Harton''' is an area of the town of [[South Shields]], in [[Tyne and Wear]], [[England]].  It is primarily a residential area, with several schools and leisure facilities, including St Wilfrid's College for Mathematics and Computing, South Shields Community School and Brinkburn Recreation Ground. [[South Tyneside District Hospital]] is also situated in the area.

It is served by [[Tyne Dock Metro station]] on the [[Tyne and Wear Metro]].

